high_descs: walk through the hallway and go to the dresser.
go to the dresser and pick up the plate that is on the top of the dresser.
take the plate to the sink in the bathroom.
Put the plate in the sink, wash the plate and then remove the plate.
walk through the hallway and go back to the dresser in the bedroom.
Put the plate on top of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Get the plate, clean it and put it back on the dresser.

high_descs: Turn left to access the passage and turn right to reach the dresser.
Pick up the plate from the dresser.
Turn left to head out the bedroom and turn right to walk down the passage and reach the bathroom sink on the left.
Wash the plate in the sink and take the plate out.
Turn right to exit the bathroom and head down the passage on the right and turn left to reach the dresser.
Put the plate on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed Plate on Dresser.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight then turn right to reach the dresser.
Go near to the table and pick the plate from the table.
Turn left and exit in the sink.
Go straight turn left to reach the plate in the sink.
Put the plate in the sink and pour the water and clean the dresser.
Take the plate go straight to reach the bed room then turn left to reach on the dresser and put the plate on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned Plate on the Dresser.
